          "source": "text:`\n\t\t\t\t\t\tUse the default navigation strategy of Obsidian.\n\t\t\t\t\t\tWhen working with multiple tab groups, \n\t\t\t\t\t\tnew tabs may appear in unexpected locations.\n\t\t\t\t\t`",
